Resolution Description: The Department of Transportation inspected this complaint and repaired the problem.

Descriptor: Branch or Limb Has Fallen Down
Resolution Description: The Department of Parks and Recreation inspected but the condition was not found.

The Department of Parks and Recreation prunes street trees on a seven year pruning cycle.  However, the Department of Parks and Recreation reviews service requests for street tree pruning and as warranted, will take immediate action to correct the condition.
The Police Department responded to the complaint and with the information available observed no evidence of the violation at that time.
